http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Quarry-owner-kidnapped-released-after-collecting-ransom/article13985908.ece

Quarry owner kidnapped, releasedAn unidentified gang on Wednesday evening kidnapped a granite quarry owner at his factory near Yadamarri, 15 km from here, and whisked him away in an SUV before abandoning him in a forest near Bangarupalem after reportedly collecting a ransom of Rs. 50 lakh. The quarry owner was identified as Bajalingam.The Yadamarri police confirmed the abduction episode and said that a criminal case would be booked against the culprits. Police officers inspected the quarry and the spot where the kidnappers freed Bajalingam.